  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b5d3e5d254f814630af75a3ff5cadf10, type: 3}
  m_Name: New Dialogue Object
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueObject
  dialogue:
  - 'Hello Young Traveler! It seems you are new around here... may I tell you of
    a great tale passed down for generations? '
  - It is foretold that the chosen one will obtain the keys and unlock the great
    north door to banish the Sentinel One.
  - Say, you want to search for these keys? Well they're just to our left and right.
  - I warn you however young traveler, there are many vicious monsters who roam these
    lands.
  - 'I would greatly advise you to pick up useful items along the way that may aid
    you in battle. '
  - 'You also might want to speak with the other townsfolk to learn more about these
    lands. '
  - Good luck young traveler. I fear you may need it.
  portrait: {fileID: -4786132149333952748, guid: e753e02afcfcc4bbc9ae4e6c75568636, type: 3}
